  goods\, and creative finds to the campus community.  Catch the vibe of a
 n Asian Night Market\, during the day!  And hang out for the AAPI Heritag
 e Month flag raising at 12:00p.m.\n \nIf you would like to be a vendor at
  the AAPI "Day" Market\, please sign up here.  Space is limited\, so sign
  up soon!\n \n\nAANHPI "DAY" MARKET\nWednesday\, April 1\, 2026\n11:00am 
 - 2:00pm\nStudent Center Quad (rain location: Student Center Ballrooms)\n
