DESCRIPTION:The Department of Art & Design invites you to From the Basemen
 t\, the BFA Visual Communications Design 2026 Graduate Exhibition. Join u
 s at the Finley Gallery from March 25 to April 7 to experience a dynamic 
 showcase of work by graduating VCDS students\, featuring posters\, motion
  graphics\, packaging\, editorial\, and more. With the opening reception 
 on Friday\, March 27\, 4 to 6pm.\n \nVenture into the world of graphic de
 sign at the VCDS 2026 graduate exhibition\, From the Basement. This exhib
 ition highlights the work of graduating Visual Communication Design stude
 nts and the projects they developed throughout their time in the VCDS BFA
  program. A range of mediums will be featured\, including posters\, motio
 n graphics\, packaging\, editorial\, and more! Together\, these works ref
 lect the unique styles and creative voices of the class.\n \nFeatured Des
 igners:\nJalen Aguirre\, Ysabella De Leon\, Brett Diese\, Domenic Faliven
 e\, Anna Fronczkowski\, Tori Gallagher\, Camila Garcia\, Robert Gaskill\,
  Britany Giraldo\, David Guerra\, Audrey Hitchens\, Natalia Kurpiewski\, 
 Paolo La Rosa\, Izzy Latella\, Katie Mascuch\, Caitlin Mendoza\, Evan Oku
 n\, Erika Oliva\, Julia Oliveri\, Christian Pajaro\, Nicole Ricci\, Chris
 topher Rizzi\, Casey Ryu\, Tom Sheridan\, Michael Shimabukuro\, Gabby Tre
 zza\, Maral Tutunjian\, and Dogan Uludogan\n \nBFA Visual Communications 
 Design Graduate Exhibition\nExhibition dates: March 25–April 7\, 2026\nOp
 ening Reception: Friday\, March 27\, 4–6pm\nFinley Gallery\, Finley Hall\
 n \nCome meet the designers and celebrate their work! Support the next ge
 neration of designers as they transition from academia into the professio
 nal world.\n\nHosted by: Art and Design\n\nAdditional Information can be 
 found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12352695
DTEND:20260401T230000Z
DTSTAMP:20260401T043556Z
DTSTART:20260401T150000Z
