DESCRIPTION:Join the Polish Club for a fun and interactive cultural event 
 celebrating Polish Easter traditions! Learn about the history and meaning
  behind Pisanki (traditional Polish Easter eggs)\, Śmigus-Dyngus\, Easter
  baskets (Święconka)\, and other holiday customs.\nParticipants will have
  the opportunity to decorate their own fake eggs using colorful paints an
 d patterns while enjoying a welcoming and creative atmosphere. This event
  is a great way to explore Polish culture\, meet new people\, and create 
 a unique keepsake to take home.\n\nHosted by: Montclair State Polish Club
 \n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.
 com/engage/event/12134340
