X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Foundation": "https://montclairfoundation.org/event/virtual-meditation-31-9/2026-04-01/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairfoundation_calendar_of_events
X-SOURCE:Montclair Foundation
X-SOURCE-URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/calendar-of-events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260401T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260401T210000
DTSTAMP:20260401T003536
CREATED:20260318T225001Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260318T225002Z
UID:10006011-1775070000-1775077200@montclairfoundation.org
SUMMARY:Virtual Meditation
DESCRIPTION:Virtual Meditation \nInstructor: John Welshons \nWednesdays\, 7:00 PM – 9:00 PM \nJanuary 7\, 14\, 21\, 28 \nFebruary 4\, 11\, 25 \nMarch 4\, 18\, 25 \nApril 1\, 8\, 15\, 22\, 29 \nMay 6\, 13\, 20 \nJune 3\, 10\, 24 \nJoin contemporary spiritual teacher and author Ramananda John E. Welshons (One Soul\, One Love\, One Heart\, When Prayers Aren’t Answered and Awakening From Grief) for a series of evening meditation classes in the comfort of your own home via Zoom. These classes will focus on specific practices for working with fear and anxiety.  Participants will learn and practice different forms of mindfulness meditation in each session and will have the opportunity to participate in discussions of Ramananda’s three critically acclaimed books. Open to beginners and experienced practitioners\, these gatherings offer an opportunity to experience deep inner peace while practicing with a highly experienced meditation teacher.  \nImportant Updated Registration Information: \nA Zoom Link will be sent the day of the class. If you are registering after 3 PM on the day of the class\, the Zoom link will be included in the automated payment confirmation email sent when you register. There is no registration deadline for this class. \nFee: Single class: $10 Members / $15 General Public
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/virtual-meditation-31-9/2026-04-01/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults,Virtual
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2024/06/outdoor-meditation-scaled.jpg
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Montclair Local News": "https://montclairlocal.news/event/back-to-all-events-breathwork-with-julie-billy/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:montclairlocal
X-SOURCE:Montclair Local News
X-SOURCE-URL:https://montclairlocal.news/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260401T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260401T200000
DTSTAMP:20260331T231044
CREATED:20260326T180827Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260326T180827Z
UID:10139426-1775070000-1775073600@montclairlocal.news
SUMMARY:Back to All Events Breathwork with Julie & Billy
DESCRIPTION:A Sacred Energy Reset.\nStep into a deeply restorative experience designed to awaken your energy\, calm your mind\, and bring your body back into balance.\nThis immersive journey begins with Qi Gong\, an ancient practice rooted in Traditional Chinese Medicine that uses slow\, intentional movement\, breathwork\, and focused awareness to cultivate and circulate life force energy (Qi). Through gentle\, flowing sequences\, you’ll release tension\, regulate your nervous system\, and reconnect to your body with ease.\nAs your energy begins to open and flow\, you’ll transition into a deeply calming sound healing experience. Guided by Vinni Taneja\, Himalayan singing bowls and resonant tones work to clear energetic blockages\, restore harmony\, and anchor you into a profound state of relaxation and inner stillness.\nAligned with the energy of renewal and new beginnings\, this practice supports you in letting go of what no longer serves you and creating space for clarity\, vitality\, and intention.\nWhat to expect:\n✨ Gentle Qi Gong movement + breathwork\n✨ Nervous system reset + energy activation\n✨ Sound healing with singing bowls\n✨ Deep relaxation + emotional clearing\n✨ Space to reconnect\, reflect\, and realign\nAbout Vinni:\nVinni Taneja is a multi-faceted healer and founder of Chakra Wellness\, integrating Qi Gong\, Reiki\, sound healing\, and holistic wellness practices to support mind-body-spirit alignment.\n📍 Loopwell · 80 Maple Ave\, Montclair\, NJ\n🗓 Tuesday\, May 19\n⏰ 7:00–8:30 PM\n🎟 $40\nCome as you are.\nLeave centered\, clear\, and deeply renewed \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/back-to-all-events-breathwork-with-julie-billy/
LOCATION:Loopwell\, 80 Maple Ave\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:General Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/March-Calendar-11.jpg
END:VEVENT
