SUMMARY:Future Pathways for the U.S. - Europe Partnership  NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nWe'll analyze the the upsides and downsides of U.S. - European 
 relations. Former U.N. communications officer Pierre Fabian will ponder 
 whether Washington should continue to spurn Europe's demands for more 
 balanced cooperation and instead choose to face a more dangerous world on 
 its own. Alternatively\, might the U.S. choose to forge a new and more 
 accommodating transatlantic relationship based on mutual understanding of 
 national interests?
LOCATION:Montclair Bellevue Ave Branch - First Floor\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School
