DESCRIPTION:The purpose of the Men About Change mental health event is to 
 raise awareness and encourage open discussion about men’s mental health c
 hallenges in today’s society. This event aims to create a supportive and 
 judgment-free space where participants can explore common mental health i
 ssues affecting men\, learn healthy coping strategies\, and gain access t
 o campus resources such as CAPS. By promoting open dialogue and education
 \, the event seeks to reduce stigma\, encourage help-seeking behavior\, a
 nd support the overall well-being of men within the campus community.\n\n
 Hosted by: Lambda Sigma Upsilon Latino Fraternity\, Inc.\n\nAdditional In
 formation can be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/
 12384801
