SUMMARY:A Magnificent Life
DTSTART:20260402T113000
DTEND:20260402T133000
UID:cec882ed03b3d9bc4062b1e19e8da08e@montclairfilm.org
DESCRIPTION:Following the life of Pagnol\, a playwright\, novelist and fil
 mmaker who grew up in a middle-class household in Marseille and became one
  of the world's most inventive and prolific artists from the 1930s to the 
 1950s.
