DESCRIPTION:Not sure what to major in or where you're headed after college
 ? Let’s change that—starting with the kind of day you want to have. In th
 is hands-on\, creative workshop\, you’ll:\n1) Visualize your ideal workda
 y—where you are\, who you’re with\, and what you’re doing.\n2) Identify y
 our key work-life preferences\, like flexibility\, collaboration\, or cre
 ativity.\n3) Explore majors and careers that align with your vision throu
 gh UC’s AI-powered Major Mentor\, a tool that matches your preferences to
  Montclair majors and career paths.\nThis event is open to all University
  College (pre-major) students. RSVP is required. There will be compliment
 ary food.\n\nHosted by: The Discovery Program\n\nAdditional Information c
 an be found at: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12025760
