SUMMARY:The Searcher's Bible Study - Thursdays 7pm on Zoom
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260402T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260402T200000
DTSTAMP:20260401T043557Z
UID:99365vs466s8le45pm9ncap089_R20251002T230000@google.com__20260402
SEQUENCE:1
CREATED:20250121T153136Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Led by FCC member and ordained pastor\, Rev. Victor Pete
 rson. This is an open study\, dedicated to exploring our sacred scriptures
