SUMMARY:[Outside Org]  Word Press
DESCRIPTION:We’re a local WordPress community where anyone\, from total 
 beginners to seasoned developers\, designers and business owners\, can come 
 learn\, share\, ask questions\, and connect. Whether you’re running a 
 WordPress website for your business\, just inherited one you’re not sure 
 where to start\, or you're curious about how websites work in general\, 
 you’ll feel right at home here.\n \n\nWe meet regularly for in-person 
 events where you can get help with your site\, chat with others in the 
 community\, and hear how other people are building and running their 
 websites. For more information on upcoming events\, visit 
 https://jerseypress.org or 
 https://www.meetup.com/WordPress-Montclair-Meetup
