SUMMARY:Good Friday Pilgrimage to Delaney Hall
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260403T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260403T153000
DTSTAMP:20260401T043557Z
UID:3gdqm091o60l3rk1602mk1n4o8@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20260403T080000
SEQUENCE:0
CREATED:20260327T224053Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><span>Join us on an ecumenical Good Friday journey from Mon
 tclair to Delaney Hall\, the ICE Detention Center in Newark. Together we w
 ill pray with our feet\, show solidarity with our immigrant neighbors\, an
 d bear witness to the cruelty towards and crucifixion of immigrants today.
 </span> </p><p><span><b>Join us starting at 8am</b> for the full 10 mile 
 walk\, or you may join in the first or last section\, or the culminating p
 rayer service at 3pm at Delaney Hall.</span></p><p><span><b>8am Gather at 
 First Congregational Church\, Montclair (40 S. Fullerton)</b><br>• Optio
 n: Join us for the first mile from FCC\, Montclair to Christ Episcopal Chu
 rch in Bloomfield/Glen Ridge</span> </p><p><span><b>1:30pm Gather at St. 
 Stephen’s Grace Community – ELCA\, Ironbound (7 Wilson Avenue Newark N
 J)</b><br>• Option: Join us for the 2 mile final leg of the journey from
  St. Stephen’s to Delaney Hall</span></p><p><span><b>3pm Prayer Service 
 at Delaney Hall\, 451 Doremus Avenue\, Newark</b></span> </p><p><span><b>
 For RSVP and accessibility info</b> </span><a href="https://docs.google.co
 m/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5kHJhWDRwg50BncOw5lU-GVPRUPQcERj74LLyE5x8Ienlcw/viewf
 orm" target="_blank"><span>CLICK HERE</span></a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260327T224110Z
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:OPAQUE
X-SOURCE:First Congregational Church Montclair
X-SOURCE-URL:https://fccmontclair.org/upcoming-events-at-fcc/
END:VEVENT
