DTSTAMP:20260401T043557Z
UID:1r0nrf7ha302e168afirmgrg2d@google.com__20260403
SEQUENCE:0
CREATED:20251016T175055Z
DESCRIPTION:We are a group of women\, roughly over the age of 65\, maybe r
 etired (whatever that looks like today)\, who meet the<strong> <u>first</u
 > Friday of each month from 11am to 1pm in the FCC library.</strong> We g
 ather to form connections and to strengthen our bonds of friendship withi
 n the FCC community. It is a time of informal conversation about anything\
 , and everything\, and nothing. Questions?  See Rev. Heather Cherrey\, o
 r email her at <a href="mailto:revcherrey@optonline.net">revcherrey@optonl
 ine.net</a>.
