X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: Metrotrails Hiking": "https://www.meetup.com/metrotrails/events/314053244/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_metrotrails
X-SOURCE:Meetup: Metrotrails Hiking
UID:event_314053244@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T043554Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T180000
SUMMARY:Passaic River Series Hike
DESCRIPTION:Metrotrails: NJ\, PA\, NY Metropolitan Area Hiking and More!\n
 Join us for the next hike in our Passaic River Series!\nThis time\, we sta
 rt where we left off following the river and its greenways as closely as p
 ossible\; we meet at Fairfield Fee Public Library\, then shuttle with as f
 ew cars as possible to our start.\nThere will be some back street walking 
 from the start\, but after not too long we will pick up the Morris Canal G
 reenway.\nFrom there\, we follow this greenway and a couple of other paths
  west past the Willowbrook Mall. Lightly used back streets take us along t
 he river and then into some of the Great Piece Meadows where we'll be on a
  trail for about 4 miles. This might be the only potentially rough section
  depending on the level of rain we get approaching the day.\nWe'll exit th
 e public lands and then take back streets a short bit to Fairfield Park\, 
 and finish with a nice bit of trail to the end.\nIf needed\, contact me at
  908 343 8374
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/metrotrails/events/314053244/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260331T115316Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260331T115316Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
