SUMMARY:Tech Help Tuesdays: One-on-One Tech Help
DESCRIPTION:Drop in during this weekly open session for technology related 
 help on using your cellphone\, tablet\, or computer.\n\n\nWant to feel more 
 confident using technology? Join us for Tech Help Tuesdays—a casual\, 
 drop-in space where adults can receive one-on-one assistance with everyday 
 tech challenges. Come prepared with questions relating to your personal 
 devices!\n\nRegistration is required as only one staff member is available 
 to assist at this time. 20-25 minutes are allotted per patron. If 
 registrations are full\, please check a future date\, as we cannot 
 accommodate walk-ins at this time.\n\nPlease note that some technological 
 issues may be above the ability of the library staff and you may be 
 referred out to a better suited tech professional. These drop-ins are not 
 professional IT services\, we cannot fix computers or smartphones.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Tower Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult Services, Computers & Technology
UID:LibCal-10306-15513876
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15513876
