SUMMARY:Singing Resistance Virtual Sing (ZOOM)
DESCRIPTION:Singing Resistance is a nonviolent grassroots organization in solidarity with the inspiring movement that has emerged in Minneapolis. \nWe believe that what the world needs right now is not fear\, anger\, and division\, but Harmony. \nWe use song as a tool for solidarity\, community care\, unification\, and spiritual resilience\, by singing together as a community and using our voices as conduits of peace and love. \n  \nLink to Register with Singing Resistance \nhttps://forms.gle/xUdkXru1hkjoDo2i8 \n  \nWe will have a Zoom Sing on Tuesday April 7: 8 – 8:45 pm https://zoom.us/j/93186208183 \n  \nQuestions\, contact: SingingResistanceNNJ@proton.me
URL:https://www.unioncong.org/event/singing-resistance-virtual-sing-zoom/
LOCATION:Zoom
CATEGORIES:All Events
END:VEVENT
