SUMMARY:Practical Spanish 3: Basic Conversation
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register. 
 \n\nThis class is for those of you who are able to communicate in Spanish 
 at a novice level\, but want to continue to improve your pronunciation and 
 your knowledge of the language while increasing your vocabulary. 
 Presentations\, conversations and dialogues will be used as techniques for 
 oral practice. Grammatical structures will be introduced and reviewed as 
 needed.\n \nTopics covered:\n\n\n	Music/songs/artists\n	Cooking/Food 
 description/Meals\n	Family\n	Daily routine with reflexive verbs/ 
 accessories\n	Past tense (preterite) of regular verbs and some irregular 
 verbs\n	Health and Well Being/Parts of 
 Body\n	Professions/Workplace\n	Clothing/Shopping\n\n\nSkip date: No class 
 on April 28\, 2026\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Classroom\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Language
