SUMMARY:Expedition to the Black Sea and Ukraine NEW - Online
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to register on 
 the Adult School website.\n\nWhat makes the Ukraine so important? The Black 
 Sea area including Ukraine has been at the center of world events for 
 thousands of years. Throughout history\, there have been waves of invaders 
 whose objective was to control this vital area. We will explore what makes 
 this area so unique and vital by investigating the Ice Age\, prehistory\, 
 invasions\, migrations\, language\, landforms\, coastline\, and modern 
 developments as well.
LOCATION:Montclair - Offsite\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School
UID:LibCal-10306-15804021
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/15804021
END:VEVENT
