 score\, trailers and viewer’s expectations. Feb. 11\, 25\, Mar. 11\, 25\, 
 May 6\, 20\, and June 3\, 17 .take place at Congregation Shomrei Emunah. 
 Apr. 8 and 22 which take place at the First Lutheran Church.
