 rning\, Government Relations and Community Affairs \, Office of Student B
 elonging\, Office for Hispanic Initiatives\, Office of Community Engageme
 nt and Partnerships\, The Office for Experiential Education and Career Co
 nnections\n\nOnline Location: https://us06web.zoom.us/j/82724283081?pwd=K
 zAjQw24vxqmzbURBXGmbBLV3V60m3.1\n\nAdditional Information can be found at
