SUMMARY:Raised Bed Gardening with Bracco Farms
DESCRIPTION:Ready to take your gardening game to the next level? Join us 
 for an engaging and informative talk all about the power of the Raised Bed 
 Garden!\n\nThis talk will be hosted by Bracco Farms. They will discuss the 
 benefits of raised garden beds include better soil drainage\, easy access 
 to plants\, portability\, soil customization increased soil control\, and 
 also the ability to keep weeds and pests at bay. Bracco Farms will discuss 
 everything from planning to growing in a Raised Bed Garden. We will 
 demonstrate how almost every kind of plant will grow better in it for many 
 reasons which we will point out. They will also bring\, show and 
 demonstrate many of the hand tools used in a Raised Bed garden.\n\nPlease 
 note this event will take place in the Main Library's Auditorium.
LOCATION:Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Library":MAILTO:events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult Services, Home & Garden
UID:LibCal-10306-16441462
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/16441462
END:VEVENT
