SUMMARY:Practical French 3
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nFrench Conversation 3 is suitable for intermediate French 
 speakers and above. Conversations are based on current events\, real life 
 situations\, culture\, travel\, and other interesting topics. Expanding 
 your vocabulary\, improving your pronunciation\, and increasing your 
 confidence in speaking are positive outcomes. Come join 
 us!\n\n\n	\n		\n			\n			 \n			\n		\n	\n
