SUMMARY:Go-Kart Racing Thrill - North Jersey
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nJoi
 n us for an hour or two of go-kart racing indoors at K1 Speed\, 670 Union 
 Boulevard. No experience is needed. All you have to do is show up!\n\nThe 
 place looks to be opening "soon\," so I'll be able to provide pricing and 
 other details as we get closer.\n\n\\*\\*\\* We typically hang out afterwa
 rd or before at a place to eat some food or grab a drink. Feel free to pos
 t suggestions below in the comments section. \\*\\*\\*\n\nIf looking to le
 arn more\, here's the website links for the go karting place: www.k1speed.
 com/totowa-location.html\n\nhttps://www.instagram.com/p/DNZCZDYyLVO/?hl=en
 &img_index=2\n\nQuestions? Suggestions? Concerns? You can message me on Me
 etup or WhatsApp\, or call/text me at 201-234-9609. Or feel free to commen
 t below.\n\nThis event idea comes to you courtesy of Oscar\, one of our ma
 ny regulars\, and also our group chat. Hope you'll consider attending our 
 first go-karting event\, or joining us for a bowling\, volleyball\, tennis
  or other event -> [www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball]
 (https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleyball)
