SUMMARY:Adult B'nai Mitzvah Class
DESCRIPTION:Rabbi James Feder will be launching a new Adult B’nei Mitzvah cohort this fall. The class will meet weekly on Sunday mornings at 11:30am with the first class on Sunday\, October 12th. Anyone interested in delving deeper into Jewish tradition and practice — whether you plan to participate in the Adult B’nei Mitzvah ceremony or not — is welcome to participate. \nThose who have already become Bar or Bat Mitzvah are also welcome to join\, as is anyone pursuing conversion. \nCost: $275 \nREGISTER HERE! \n 
