SUMMARY:Journaling in the Garden
DESCRIPTION:Journaling in the Garden \nMonthly on Mondays\, 12:00 PM – 1:00 PM. (Series or individual Classes) \nApril 13th \nMay 11th \nJune 15th \nExplore the beauty of the Van Vleck Gardens this spring through reflective writing and creative mark-making.  This mindfulness-based class/series invites you to slow down\, observe the natural world and turn your blank pages into a wonderland of personal observations.  Each class takes place in a different area of the Gardens (weather permitting)\, offering new inspiration for discovery.  Deepen your connection with nature and yourself in a no-pressure environment.  No art or writing experience necessary – just an openness to explore\, reflect and create.   \nFee: Series Rate (4 classes): $50 Members / $70 General Public \nIndividual Rate: $15 Members / $20 General Public \nRegistration required by 1 day prior to class.
URL:https://montclairfoundation.org/event/journaling-in-the-garden-2/2026-04-13/
LOCATION:Van Vleck House & Gardens\, 21 Van Vleck Street\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Adults
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairfoundation.org/content/uploads/2026/01/nature-journaling-1-e1768316290510.jpg
END:VEVENT
