SUMMARY:Mah Jongg Self-Paced Learning Space - Weekly Monday Morning - NEW
DESCRIPTION:The Mah Jongg Self-Paced Learning Space provides a weekly 
 opportunity for teaching yourself the basics of American Mah Jongg at your 
 own pace.\n\nThe library will provide the book Beginner's Guide to American 
 Mah Jongg by Elaine Sandberg\, Mah Jongg card\, a set and table!  You can 
 also boost your learning with a list of  Mah Jongg resources available at 
 the library. \n\nAfter you know the basics of Mah Jongg\, and would like to 
 play the game with other Mah Jongg players\, please register for the "Mah 
 Jongg Meetup" by clicking here. \n
LOCATION:Montclair Bellevue Ave Branch - Classroom
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Bellevue Avenue Branch":MAILTO:branch-events@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult Services, Bellevue Avenue Branch
