DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260413T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260413T213000
SUMMARY:Meeting at the Verona inn!
DESCRIPTION:Board Game Night At Verona Inn\nWe will be doing our first mon
 thly meeting starting on **February 25th at the Verona Inn!** We will be m
 eeting up to organize games starting at 7:30\, with food and drinks availa
 ble! You can play any game provided by hosts or bring your own! If you do 
 not have a friend group to play games\, hosts will organize you into pods 
 with other people who need players. There are **no dues**. Future meetings
  will be held on the **last Wednesday of each month.**\n\nMore information
  and ground rules:\n\n* **The doors open at 6:30 but games do not start un
 til 7:30.** I *highly recommend* coming in during this period to eat your 
 food and drink ahead of time!\n*\n* **Please return the graciousness provi
 ded by our hosts and order at least one item! All venue specific rules app
 ly to our club.** Future meetings depend on treating our hosts with respec
 t.\n* **All games must be returned to their owners when they announce that
  they are leaving.** If you are in a game in progress when the meeting end
 s but it is not borrowed you may continue playing!\n* **Please place food 
 and drink on a separate table or surface from your games** to help avoid s
 tains and other damage.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/board-game-night-at-verona-inn/events
 /313287511/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260209T235052Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260209T235052Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
