SUMMARY:Leaving a Legacy: Family and Organization Histories
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nIf you don't tell your story\, who will?  Learn how to start 
 and what's involved in capturing the history of your family or organization 
 for posterity.  We'll cover content\, research methods\, formats\, use of 
 outside writers and editors\, publishing possibilities\, and more.
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Conference Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
