SUMMARY:Stretch\, Resistance & Light Cardio
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nAccording to medical professionals\, it is important to keep 
 the body flexible & the bones strong. The synovial fluid in our joints is 
 extremely important for good movement. Strong muscles act like shock 
 absorbers to protect our bones. With resistance exercises\, the bones and 
 muscles will remain strong or even become stronger. Light hand & leg 
 weights optional. \n
LOCATION:Montclair - First Lutheran Church\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Fitness
