DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nDiscover how to truly see through the act of drawing. In this 
 hands-on class\, you’ll learn the basics of line\, form\, value\, scale 
 and composition while learning to capture what you observe. We’ll explore 
 traditional drawing techniques that will help you create a foundation 
 towards your own unique way of expressive mark-making. All skill levels of 
 adult learning are welcomed.\n
