DTSTART:20260416T143000Z
DTEND:20260416T160000Z
DTSTAMP:20260416T000000Z
SUMMARY:The Twilight Zone: The Supernatural: Enchanted Objects - Mystical Forces NEW
DESCRIPTION:This is a paid Adult School class. Click here to 
 register.\n\nNothing says The Twilight Zone like stories about enchanted 
 objects\, mystical forces or the presence of magic. Though they are 
 interesting elements in the stories\, the real intrigue lies with how the 
 episodes’ characters behave in their presence. Driven by desperation\, 
 curiosity or just plain fear\, we get the opportunity to witness lessons 
 learned whether the result is salvation or human downfall.\n\n\nDuring five 
 episodes\, we will see various responses to the unexplained. Whether they 
 are controlled by superstition\, are mishandling seemingly ordinary objects 
 or dismissing what is not fully understood\, each character must face the 
 life-changing consequences\nof their decisions.\n\n\nPlease join Linda 
 Hetcher this season in the interactive study of the supernatural\, most 
 notably presented in The Twilight Zone.\n
LOCATION:Montclair Main - Conference Room\, Montclair Public Library
ORGANIZER;CN="Montclair Adult School":MAILTO:adultschool@montclairlibrary.org
CATEGORIES:Adult School, Books, Film & Theater
UID:LibCal-10306-16247104
URL:https://bccls.libcal.com/event/16247104
END:VEVENT
