SUMMARY:Shomrei Gives Back - Mitzvah Day
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T093000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T123000
DTSTAMP:20260328T020314Z
UID:TU1892966145
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T093000
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Events
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20250605T135433Z
DESCRIPTION:**2nd Annual Mitzvah Day**  \n  \nGather as a community in ser
 vice to perform mitzvot for our local social action partners\, Israel\, an
 d Shomrei itself. All ages welcome! There is a Mitzvah for everyone\, incl
 uding kids! Babysitting available for 1st grade and under. Breakfast nosh 
 provided.  \n  \nOpen to Shomrei Community &amp\; Your Friends.  \n  \n**P
 articipate in any or all activities:**   \n  \nDONATE SUPPLIES** Donate it
 ems needed to make our Mitzvot a reality. Visit our online wish list to ma
 ke a purchase. Make sure items are delivered to Shomrei **by April 8.** Dr
 op-offs at Shomrei are welcome. Or\, fund the supplies with a monetary don
 ation. You don't have to donate items to participate (but it helps!)  \n**
 online wish list: https://shomrei.org/wishlist**  \n**alternative monetary
  donation:** **https://shomrei.org/supplies**  \n **VOLUNTEER YOUR TIME on
  April 19:**  \n- Assemble Senior grocery bags for Toni's Kitchen\n- Sort 
 donated spring &amp\; summer clothes for Human Needs Food Pantry\n- Assemb
 le "Welcome to Your New Home" kits for Family Promise\n- Make sandwiches f
 or MESH\n- Garden outdoors at Shomrei\n- Make friendship bracelets for a s
 chool in Israel (kid-specific)\n- Color pictures/write letters for seniors
  (kid-specific)\n- Write thank you cards for pet adoptions for the Montcla
 ir Animal Shelter (kid-specific)\n\n  \n**register here: https://shomrei.o
 rg/mitzvah  \n  \n**PARTICIPATE IN A DRIVE**  \nBring breakfast cereals an
 d/or adult and children’s summer clothing for Human Needs Food Pantry to
  Shomrei (Drop off at Shomrei or bring with you on Mitzvah day.)  \n  \nKe
 y fob required for building entry.  \n   \n**Questions?**  \nContact the O
 ffice  \noffice@shomrei.org  \n(973) 746-5031\n\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20260318T044627Z
TRANSP:OPAQUE
URL;VALUE=URI:https://teamup.com/kstx8swyw669kakgqa/events/1892966145
X-SOURCE:Congregation Shomrei Emunah
X-SOURCE-URL:https://shomrei.org/calendar/
END:VEVENT
