 s\, bobcat\, and lynx!\nHow do I sign-up?\n\nRegistration opens on Fusion
  March 1st\nRegister online through Fusion\, in the Student Recreation Ce
 nter's main office\, or over the phone (973-655-3340).\nCost for Students
  $10\; Faculty/Staff $20\n\nWhen and where?\n\nSunday\, April 19\, 2026\n
 12:00 pm - 5:00 pm\nBegins at Student Recreation Center\n\nWhat to bring:
  Water\, lunch\, long pants\, sneakers\, and sunscreen.\nPotential Hazard
 s: Unpredictable weather changes\, sunburn/heat exhaustion\, dehydration\
 , allergic reactions/poisonous plants\, insect bites and injury by runnin
 g\, including sprains\, lacerations\, abrasions and fractures. \n\nHosted
  by: Campus Recreation\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https:/
 /montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12179794
