 rsday from 3:30–4:45 PM\, tap in for weekly discussions that spark conver
 sation\, inspire change\, and build community.\nFrom civil rights and men
 tal health to campus advocacy and organizing\, each week features a new t
 opic rooted in the NAACP’s mission. Whether you want to speak up\, listen
 \, or just vibe with like-minded students\, this is your space. Come as y
 ou are—everyone belongs here. 🖤\n\nHosted by: National Association for t
 he Advancement of Colored People\n\nAdditional Information can be found a
 t: https://montclair.campuslabs.com/engage/event/12176442
