X-SOURCE:Meetup: NJ Bowling, Volleyball, Tennis & More
UID:event_314009464@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T043555Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T133000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260425T153000
SUMMARY:Casual Volleyball - North Jersey
DESCRIPTION:North Jersey Bowling\, Volleyball\, Tennis And More (BVT)\nWe'
 re a group of people who will start by hitting the ball around for the fir
 st 20-30 minutes and then we'll break up into 2-4 teams for two or three h
 ours of play.\n\nIf we have more than 20 people show up\, we'll break up i
 nto three or four teams of 6 (Some may have 7\, 8 or 9. Additional players
  just rotate into play). Games will be to 10 points. Rally scoring. Winner
  stays on (unless a team has won four straight).\n\nWe'll be heading outdo
 ors to the hard court in Leonia off Overpeck County Pk Driveway in the Ove
 rpeck County Park.\n\n\\*\\*\\* After playing\, we'll be likely heading to
  Tropical Juice Bar\, an idea of regular attendee Kate\, for a drink and s
 nack. It's located at 60 River St. in Hackensack. Feel free to join us or 
 suggest another spot for a post-volleyball hangout. \\*\\*\\*\n\nThere's n
 o fee to play volleyball and nothing else you need to do besides show up. 
 Come anytime!! All are welcome!!! We're not in a league and are not here t
 o analyze your form. We're more for people who haven't played in months\, 
 maybe years\, and just want to occasionally play again and hang out.\n\nDi
 rections: You can Google "Volleyball Court in Leonia" and it should come u
 p. Or type 41 Willow Tree Road\, Leonia\, NJ 07605 into your GPS\, but not
 e that it's not on Willow Tree Road\, just near it. Instead\, turn onto Ov
 erpeck County Pk Driveway off Fort Lee Road (Degraw Avenue). It is past th
 e tennis courts and near a basketball court and track. You can try Googlin
 g Leonia High School as well. That should help you find it.\n\nWe don't ha
 ve the court reserved and if it happens to be taken\, we may play with tho
 se already occupying it or we will try to relocate on the fly. It's certai
 nly possible that we may have to cancel that day if we can't find a suitab
 le spot. Please keep that in mind. And if it's looking like it'll rain or 
 snow\, I'll make a call on whether to cancel around an hour ahead of time.
 \n\nPlease bring a ball and net if you have them for possible use during t
 he game. Feel free to bring a speaker for music\, or snacks and drinks for
  consumption during play.\n\nIf you have trouble finding the court or grou
 p\, you can call or text Andy Milone at 201-234-9609. There is plenty of p
 arking and an open bathroom at the park.\n\nHope you'll join us for our 18
 th volleyball event. Questions or comments? You can message Andy on Meetup
 \, or call/text him at 201-234-9609.\n\nCheck out bowling\, soccer\, volle
 yball\, tennis or one of our other activities at: www.meetup.com/north-jer
 sey-bowling-soccer-volleyball
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-jersey-bowling-soccer-volleybal
 l/events/314009464/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260329T005136Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260329T005136Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
