DESCRIPTION: \n\n\nVisiting the Pantry:\n1) Please have your Event Pass\, 
 CWID and have a PantrySoft Registration. 2) Please bring your own shoppin
 g bag and ID card!***Visitors are allowed to come once/week***\nOur Missi
 on:  We aim to address food insecurity across Montclair State University.
  The Red Hawk Pantry is open to all students\, staff\, and faculty at no 
 cost. If you are unable to visit during our regular hours\, please reach 
 out via email at redhawkpantry@montclair.eduStay updated by following us 
 on Instagram: @montclair_redhawkpantry\n \n🍎 Fall 2025 Hours\n\nMondays:
