DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260502T120000
SUMMARY:Fairy Trail Day 2026
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\n**Join Us 
 for the Fourth Annual Fairy Trail Day!**\n\nThe fairies of the South Mount
 ain Reservation invite you to our **4th Annual Fairy Tales on the Fairy Tr
 ail**! This festival-style event promises a day filled with fun and magic\
 , including: storytelling\, fairy house building\, fairy hair\, a magical 
 scavenger hunt and more!\n\nWings\, crowns\, and t-shirts will be availabl
 e for purchase\, with all proceeds benefiting the South Mountain Reservati
 on Fairy Trail.\n\nDress up in your sparkliest attire\, complete with crow
 ns and wings (or purchase them at the event)\, and let’s celebrate the m
 agic of the Fairy Trail together!\n\nAll proceeds go directly to the SMC F
 airy Trail Fund.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313545916/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260226T213432Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T213432Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
