 ongregation at Montclair? </li><li>Visiting or "Congregation Shopping" fo
 r yourself or your family? </li><li>Want to know a bit more about our con
 gregation and the Unitarian Universalist tradition?</li></ul><br>Join with
  one of our ministers and other newcomers to for a short\, honest\, in-dep
 th conversation. All of your questions will be honored. Children age 12 an
 d above are welcome to participate.<u></u><u></u>
