SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T043553Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260621T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260621T113000
SUMMARY:Forest Regeneration Volunteer Workday
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\nForest Reg
 eneration activities focus on the areas in and around the fenced 14-acre F
 orest and Wildflower Preserve located near the Dog Park on Bear Lane in th
 e Reservation. On workdays\, we focus on removing invasive plants like kno
 tweed\, garlic mustard and mugwort. Ages 12 to 15 are welcome with a paren
 t or guardian present. Ages 15 and above require a signature by a parent o
 r guardian on a [liability waiver](https://1drv.ms/b/c/d5fb9d3835660a78/IQ
 CJO4IIj6GnQ6N4RuNC981xAYL2kFajs9_RL8f8V7NkhaM?e=5bd5oi)\; teenagers cannot
  just be dropped off.\n\nPlease arrive 5 to 10 minutes early so we can hik
 e into the Wildflower Preserve at 9 am sharp.\n\nPlease dress appropriatel
 y! There is some poison ivy on trails and in work areas. Wear long pants\,
  long-sleeved shirt\, closed-toe shoes or rain boots\, bug spray\, and lay
 er as needed. We supply tools. If you have gloves\, bring them or you can 
 borrow a pair from us. Bring your own water.\n\nYou can download a copy of
  our [liability waiver](https://1drv.ms/b/c/d5fb9d3835660a78/IQCJO4IIj6GnQ
 6N4RuNC981xAYL2kFajs9_RL8f8V7NkhaM?e=5bd5oi) to print\, sign and bring to 
 the event.\n\nWe occasionally use photos of events in promotional material
 s and social media. By attending the event\, I consent to photos of me bei
 ng used in promotional materials or on social media.\n\nFor information\, 
 contact program co-coordinators Rich Rockwell and Tom Pollard at forestreg
 en@[somocon.org](http://somocon.org/)\n\nTo see what's blooming in the Wil
 dflower Preserve\, check out our [Wildflower Preserve](https://www.inatura
 list.org/projects/south-mountain-conservancy-wildflower-preserve) project 
 on iNaturalist project.\n\n**Meet at the tool sheds at the Dog Park at 12 
 Bear Lane\, Maplewood NJ**\n**GPS:** 40.739791\, -74.289181
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313786760/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260315T212339Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260315T212339Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
