BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-ID:gcal_id8bbkkkfmscdavi2jilkb2muo
SUMMARY:The Searcher's Bible Study - Thursdays 7pm on Zoom
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260625T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260625T200000
DTSTAMP:20260401T043557Z
UID:99365vs466s8le45pm9ncap089_R20251002T230000@google.com__20260625
SEQUENCE:1
CREATED:20250121T153136Z
DESCRIPTION:<span>Led by FCC member and ordained pastor\, Rev. Victor Pete
 rson. This is an open study\, dedicated to exploring our sacred scriptures
  in an accessible and engaging community.  No prior Bible experience requ
 ired! </span><span><span> </span></span><span><span> </span></span><br><s
