X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: South Mountain Conservancy": "https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313786761/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_somocon
X-SOURCE:Meetup: South Mountain Conservancy
UID:event_313786761@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T043553Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260719T090000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260719T113000
SUMMARY:Forest Regeneration Volunteer Workday
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\nForest Reg
 eneration activities focus on the areas in and around the fenced 14-acre F
 orest and Wildflower Preserve located near the Dog Park on Bear Lane in th
 e Reservation. On workdays\, we focus on removing invasive plants like kno
 tweed\, garlic mustard and mugwort. Ages 12 to 15 are welcome with a paren
 t or guardian present. Ages 15 and above require a signature by a parent o
 r guardian on a [liability waiver](https://1drv.ms/b/c/d5fb9d3835660a78/IQ
 CJO4IIj6GnQ6N4RuNC981xAYL2kFajs9_RL8f8V7NkhaM?e=5bd5oi)\; teenagers cannot
  just be dropped off.\n\nPlease arrive 5 to 10 minutes early so we can hik
 e into the Wildflower Preserve at 9 am sharp.\n\nPlease dress appropriatel
 y! There is some poison ivy on trails and in work areas. Wear long pants\,
  long-sleeved shirt\, closed-toe shoes or rain boots\, bug spray\, and lay
 er as needed. We supply tools. If you have gloves\, bring them or you can 
 borrow a pair from us. Bring your own water.\n\nYou can download a copy of
  our [liability waiver](https://1drv.ms/b/c/d5fb9d3835660a78/IQCJO4IIj6GnQ
 6N4RuNC981xAYL2kFajs9_RL8f8V7NkhaM?e=5bd5oi) to print\, sign and bring to 
 the event.\n\nWe occasionally use photos of events in promotional material
 s and social media. By attending the event\, I consent to photos of me bei
 ng used in promotional materials or on social media.\n\nFor information\, 
 contact program co-coordinators Rich Rockwell and Tom Pollard at forestreg
 en@[somocon.org](http://somocon.org/)\n\nTo see what's blooming in the Wil
 dflower Preserve\, check out our [Wildflower Preserve](https://www.inatura
 list.org/projects/south-mountain-conservancy-wildflower-preserve) project 
 on iNaturalist project.\n\n**Meet at the tool sheds at the Dog Park at 12 
 Bear Lane\, Maplewood NJ**\n**GPS:** 40.739791\, -74.289181
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313786761/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260315T212340Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260315T212340Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Meetup: WordPress Montclair": "https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/events/311737726/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:meetup_wordpress_montclair_meetup
X-SOURCE:Meetup: WordPress Montclair
X-SOURCE-URL:https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/
UID:event_311737726@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260401T043601Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260723T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260723T200000
SUMMARY:Help Desk - Bring Your Laptop\, Yourself\, and Your WordPress Prob
 lems
DESCRIPTION:WordPress Montclair Meetup\nIf you are running a WordPress sit
 e and are having issues and would like some help\, then this Meetup is for
  you!\n\nIf you know some things\, expert or not\, and want to give back t
 o the WordPress community\, then this Meetup is for you too!\n\nWe will do
  our best to match a problem with a problem-solver. On-site and in real-ti
 me. Just bring yourself\, your laptop\, and your WordPress problems.\n\nIt
 's OK if you attend and only want to observe. We recognize this is how peo
 ple learn. Given our time limit of two hours\, we may not be able to solve
  everyone's issues\, but we will try! If you are seeking help\, please com
 e prepared. Have your web site loaded in a browser\, have your WordPress a
 dmin ready\, along with a short list of issues you are trying to solve.\n\
 nPeople helping are volunteers and may not be experts. There is risk to br
 eaking your site! Please do not bring client or business sites that can im
 pact reputations or revenue. If you have a staging site we can test things
  with\, that is always preferred. If it is a production site\, please crea
 te a site backup before having someone do any work on your site.\n\nIf you
  cannot find the group\, please ask the front desk where the WordPress mee
 tup group is meeting.\n\n**PARKING**:\nWe've been asked to not park in the
  United Way lot behind the library as it could result in a parking ticket.
  Please find street parking or a parking deck.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\nJoin the **Je
 rseyPress Slack** group to chat with others in our community and get help:
  [https://jerseypress.org/slack/](https://jerseypress.org/slack/)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/wordpress-montclair-meetup/events/311
 737726/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20251027T204810Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251027T204810Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
